{"tid":1519593,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突破盲腸) 屌都唔知你哋驚啲乜","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T19:03:12.000Z","uid":86114,"like":829,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab535b74590b967ac7cbdaa5c98297c6a1e0a10","tid":1519593,"uid":86114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"大大拿拿有二百萬人係到 驚條春咩<br />\n再加上政府e家係咁要人督灰 散播白色恐怖<br />\n佢哋就係想滅聲 減少人出 做唔到國際宣傳 咁佢哋就交到貨<br />\n我地只要好似上次 170萬落雨都照出 就贏<br />\n乜鬼嘢最後一戰 解放軍 緊急法<br />\n林鄭真係出緊急法 佢就真係攬炒之母<br />\n仲有咩冇前線 <br />\n近排好多偽前線都上到前線<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">企硬! 一定贏!</span><br />\n怯你就輸成世 同埋點對得住啲義士<br />\n請緊記 6位以死明志 爆眼 新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d13cd3bd1d9624c9ef4899add9eecac634b633","tid":1519593,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"251a931d0706aa48c5103856e5448a7cebd3dacc","tid":1519593,"uid":212182,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"人多就係安全！"},{"pid":"e20d308abdc424c9433cf534bdc3f38a9217a283","tid":1519593,"uid":128995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"aa55c68df55d6d97a5604067f4670d16ab7e0a2a","tid":1519593,"uid":86114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5dcf3b1fbcda33caeef918a315322bad012c690f","tid":1519593,"uid":86114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ca8cbdaf881903be83dc0b988baa02e3e35c318e","tid":1519593,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/